{"tid":1298281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位，其實抗爭係有限期，而個限期比想像中短","createTime":"2019-07-08T23:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:31:24.000Z","uid":45118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2037fa3678e060274fd4ac4095cc742455d013","tid":1298281,"uid":45118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到，而家會有咁多行動，一呼百應，其中一個原因係學校放暑假，大專sem break<br />\n到9月開學，仲會唔會有咁多同學仔有時間做文宣，打網絡輿論戰，甚至長期野餐？<br />\n只要時間一到，就可以話社會已經消化了解呢條條例，衝擊事件以及人數都已經減少及下降，短期內可恢復二讀呢條無撤回過嘅條例，加上「粵港澳3年內設信用評分制度」，大家可以邊度都唔洗去，共享大灣區繁榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be127e59129027d704eccbb43940c363ba59837","tid":1298281,"uid":45118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTBCNyp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTBCNyp.png&h=25caaf30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我終於明白呢啲言論點嚟，原來係幫自己加緊分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19237a04d83efb82c8d597a9b7ea23df1cc24f5","tid":1298281,"uid":45118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:07:34.000Z","msg":"利申，80後廢老，中資公司返工<br />\n每次有事發生只可以睇直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地呢班後生做緊嘅野，其實好影響我2047退休係返屋企定入集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d634a131ac3b0dfde0f326c4dad0091aaefdcf9","tid":1298281,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:31:24.000Z","msg":"政府就係知呢樣野<br />\n咩都唔做係到拖"}]}